No. 658. School District No. 11, Dakota County, Neb., Petitioner, v. Edward H. Chapman et al., Administrators, etc. April 15, 1907. Mr. Elbert H. Hubbard for petitioner. No appearance for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
